RECTOR (Visual Repair)**\n- 'ክልሰ' was corrected to 'ክልስ' based on common Amharic vocabulary and likely OCR error.\n- No other significant visual OCR errors or attached punctuation were found that required correction.\n\n**PROTOCOL 4: THE LEMMATIZER (Global Citation Form)**\n- Roots were accurately identified for all valid words, e.g., 'ዕፀዋት' -> 'ዕፅ', 'ክልክላ' -> 'መከልከል', 'ክሓርሱ' -> 'ማረስ', 'ክሚጓጓዘው' -> 'ማጓጓዝ', 'ክምሰራ' -> 'መስራት', 'ክረምታዊ' -> 'ክረምት'.\n- For 'ክሎራ', the root 'ክሎሪን' was provided as a scholarly guess for its full form, as 'ክሎራ' often appears in compounds or as a shortened form.\n\n**PROTOCOL 7: THE FILTER (Size Constraint)**\n- All processed words and their roots met the minimum two-character length requirement.","input_words":["ክልልአገር","ክልልእርሳቸው","ክልልዕፀዋት","ክልሎችዋ","ክልሎችየደቡብ","ክልሰ","ክልሰት","ክልሰና","ክልተኣውላዕሎ","ክልቶክሳይድ","ክልአተ","ክልኤመንትያ","ክልኤድራባዊ","ክልክላ","ክልዔ","ክሎራ","ክሓርሱ","ክሚራ","ክሚጓጓዘው","ክምሩንም","ክምሰራ","ክምብር","ክረምታዊ","ክረምትንም","ክረሶቲል","ክረዜማ","ክሩሲየስ","ክሩፓ","ክሪም","ክሪምስ"],"batch_number":null,"batch_label":null,"model_version":"gemini-2.5-flash"},{"id":"542b6a27-7e7f-4108-90a4-2c2ad7338031","created_at":"2026-03-03T22:46:45.559084+00:00","word":null,"source_file":"rare_words_25/chunk_0090.txt","batch_index":0,"words":[{"pos":"Noun","root":"ክሊኒክ","word":"ክሊኒካስ","synonyms":["clinics","medical centers"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Adjective","root":"ክሊኒክ","word":"ክሊኒካዊ","synonyms":["clinical","medical"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Proper Noun","root":"ክሊንተን","word":"ክሊንተንን","synonyms":["Clinton"],"importance":8},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ክሊኒክ","word":"ክሊንኩ","synonyms":["the clinic"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Proper Noun","root":"ክሊፎርድ","word":"ክሊፎርድ","synonyms":["Clifford"],"importance":8},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ክሊፕ","word":"ክሊፕህ","synonyms":["your clip"],"importance":6},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ክላሽንኮቭ","word":"ክላሽንኮቮች","synonyms":["Kalashnikovs"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ክላሽንኮቭ","word":"ክላሽንኮቮች","synonyms":["Kalashnikovs"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Proper Noun","root":"ክላተን","word